INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (55,1,'2010-04-15 15:35:13','2010-04-15 14:35:13','I had to fix a bug today where the client reported that the dates on a page were all in French. She had set her browser language to French (apparently without realising).\n\nLocalisation is an area that I am ashamedly unfamiliar with, so I did some digging.\n\nI set my browser language to French (fr) and sure enough the dates appeared in French. I looked at Thread.CurrentThread.CurrentCulture.EnglishName and that was \"French\", so the culture was being picked up from the browser.\n\nAs this site is not set up for localisation, I opted to override the current culture in the web.config:\n<pre class=\"brush:csharp\">&lt;configuration&gt;\n    &lt;system.web&gt;\n        &lt;globalization culture=\"en-GB\" uiCulture=\"en-GB\" /&gt;\n    &lt;/system.web&gt;\n&lt;/configuration&gt;</pre>\n<blockquote>The culture attribute enables you to define the culture to use for processing incoming requests, whereas the uiCulture attribute enables you define the default culture needed to process any resource files in the application. (Pro. ASP.Net 3.5)</blockquote>\nThat fixed my bug and the code stayed the same but gave me an English date for the GB culture.\n<pre class=\"brush:csharp\">CurrentItem.Published.ToLongDateString()</pre>','DateTime, ToString(), and CurrentCulture','','inherit','open','open','','35-autosave','','','2010-04-15 15:35:13','2010-04-15 14:35:13','',35,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/15/35-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (56,1,'2010-04-15 15:37:48','2010-04-15 14:37:48','<strong>Just an EPiServer site</strong>\n\nOpen Visual Studio 2008 and create a new project using the EPiServer Project template. The visual studio template comes bundled with the main EPiServer 6 download.\n\nNext, create a new database. Open the EPiServer Deployment Center, and select Install SQL Server Database. Update teh website connection string with the new database details.\n\nCubeworksEPiServer6\n!4u2kn0w\n\nNext, go to the website properties page, and on the Web tab, remove the virtual path. And in the EPiServer.config file change the siteUrl in the siteSettings element.\n\nNow you should be able to launch the website and navigate to <strong>http://localhost:6666/EPiServer </strong>\n\n<strong>Move the Program Files</strong>\n\nThe EPiServer.config file contains a virtualPath section, with provider entries that have paths to files on your local drive. This will be a problem when you try to check in the website to source control, or publish the webiste.\n\nTo fix this we need to copy the files to the website folder and specify a new provider type.\n\nCopy the whole EPiServer folder from C:\\Program Files (x86)\\EPiServer to your website directory. I want to keep the folder structure in tact, the less I have to tinker with it the better I think.\n\nNext update the EPiServer.config provider entries, for example:\n\n&lt;add name=\"UIFiles\" virtualPath=\"~/EPiServer/CMS/\" physicalPath=\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\EPiServer\\CMS\\6.0.530.0\\Application\\UI\\CMS\" type=\"EPiServer.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathNonUnifiedProvider,EPiServer\" /&gt;\n\nbecomes\n\n&lt;add name=\"UIFiles\" virtualPath=\"~/EPiServer/CMS/\" physicalPath=\"~\\EPiServer\\CMS\\6.0.530.0\\Application\\UI\\CMS\" type=\"RelativePathProvider, MyEPiServer6Site\" /&gt;\n\nNotice I have changed the type of provider to RelativePathProvider, which is this:\n<pre class=\"brush:csharp\">\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>public class RelativePathProvider : EPiServer.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathNonUnifiedProvider</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>{</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>public RelativePathProvider(string providerName, NameValueCollection configParameters)</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>: base(providerName, FixConfig(configParameters))</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>{</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>}</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>private static NameValueCollection FixConfig(NameValueCollection configParameters)</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>{</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>var virtualPath = configParameters[\"physicalPath\"] ?? String.Empty;</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>if(virtualPath.StartsWith(\"~\"))</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>configParameters[\"physicalPath\"] = HostingEnvironment.MapPath(virtualPath);</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>return configParameters;</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>}</div>\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span>}</div>\npublic class RelativePathProvider : EPiServer.Web.Hosting.VirtualPathNonUnifiedProvider\n	{\n		public RelativePathProvider(string providerName, NameValueCollection configParameters)\n			: base(providerName, FixConfig(configParameters))\n		{\n		}\n\n		private static NameValueCollection FixConfig(NameValueCollection configParameters)\n		{\n			var virtualPath = configParameters[\"physicalPath\"] ?? String.Empty;\n\n			if(virtualPath.StartsWith(\"~\"))\n				configParameters[\"physicalPath\"] = HostingEnvironment.MapPath(virtualPath);\n\n			return configParameters;\n		}\n	}<span style=\"font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 19px; white-space: normal;\">\n</span></span></pre>','Creating a new EPiServer 6 Solution','','inherit','open','open','','50-revision-5','','','2010-04-15 15:37:48','2010-04-15 14:37:48','',50,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/15/50-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0);
